144
00:09:43,125 --> 00:09:45,377
- A fruit fly.
- Yes.

145
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:47,462
Oh. Oh, oh...

146
00:09:47,545 --> 00:09:51,383
You were a consort to Rasputin
and his 14-inch...

