if I didn't at least offer it to you.

154
00:10:34,091 --> 00:10:38,346
- She had great taste.
- Hmm. Where do you think I got it from?

155
00:10:41,849 --> 00:10:43,059
What's this?

156
00:10:46,646 --> 00:10:49,691
Look at it. Open it up.

157
00:10:53,069 --> 00:10:57,657
