- It wasn't good.
- I know.

173
00:12:20,657 --> 00:12:23,993
Is that what you're gonna do here,
after she dies?

174
00:12:25,537 --> 00:12:28,581
Cross everything out...
because it wasn't good?

175
00:12:34,128 --> 00:12:36,130
You're not going to get me
to talk about my mother.

176
00:12:40,217 --> 00:12:42,345
I hope not.

177
00:12:42,429 --> 00:12:44,221
Hatred's ugly.

178
00:12:44,306 --> 00:12:46,558
It's too beautiful a day for that.

179
00:12:48,393 --> 00:12:50,061
Back to the salt mines.

180
